Mail-Barracuda-API version 1.00
===============================

Mail::Barracuda::API implements the management API for the Barracuda
Spam Firewall appliances. It lets you programmatically add, modify, and remove
email addresses and domains from a Barracuda Appliance.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
	XML::Simple
	LWP::Simple::Post
  

